data.title: Heritage Building, Pedder Road
data.meta_description: A glimpse of the opulent lifestyle of the rich and famous families of  a bygone era in Mumbai. Some of these houses still survive looking incongruous surrounded by gleaming glass towers and new development and hemmed in by flyovers. This house was captured at the end of Kemps Coner Flyover on Pedder Road.
